column2: SELECT n.objid, m.rmapid, m.ra as ra, m.dec as dec, s.z as z_spec, m.z_lambda as zlambda, m.lamda as lamda,s.velDisp, s.velDispZ, o.deVRad_r, o.deVAB_r, o.deVPhi_r,o.deVMag_r, o.petroR9#_r, o.petroR5#_r, n.distance,  m.p_cen0 as p_cen, m.Dn4# as Dn4#, m.HdeltaA as HdeltaA, m.MtoLz as MtoLz,  m.logAge as logAge, m.muxtan as muxtan, m.Metal as Metal, m.Fracstar as Fracstar    into mydb.MyTable_radius2 from myDB.redmapper_mstar as m     cross apply dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) as n     join Galaxy as o on n.objid=o.objID          join SpecObj as s on n.objid=s.bestobjID
